<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-76-0712 </DOCNO><TEXT>Recent advances in the state of the art of anti-missile and anit-satellite(ASAT) technologies are discussed in this book. The various programsbeing pursued, with proposed financing, under the Administration's StrategicDefense Initiative (SDI) are also detailed. Parts and selected chaptersare: Strategic Defense Initiative (SDI); Directed Energy Weapon Technology;Kinetic Energy Weapon Technology; Ballistic Missile Defense; AlternativeFuture Scenarios; and Anti-Satellite Defense Technology.</TEXT></DOC>